    <title>迟来的实习总结</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/08/04/%E8%BF%9F%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/08/04/%E8%BF%9F%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</id>
    <published>2019-08-04T03:55:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-08-04T04:03:08.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>说出来你可能不信，昨天是我生日，我男朋友不记得，我竟然没和他吵架<br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="关系型数据库和非关系型数据库"><a href="#关系型数据库和非关系型数据库" class="headerlink" title="关系型数据库和非关系型数据库"></a>关系型数据库和非关系型数据库</h1><p><a href="https://juejin.im/post/5cbc13b06fb9a0685a3f014a?utm_source=gold_browser_extension" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://juejin.im/post/5cbc13b06fb9a0685a3f014a?utm_source=gold_browser_extension</a></p><h1 id="Ruby中的-is-a-kind-of-instance-of"><a href="#Ruby中的-is-a-kind-of-instance-of" class="headerlink" title="Ruby中的 is_a? kind_of? instance_of?"></a>Ruby中的 is_a? kind_of? instance_of?</h1><p>这是个年代有点久远的帖子，下面有一条答案有点冷酷，哈哈，喜欢<br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3893278/ruby-kind-of-vs-instance-of-vs-is-a" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3893278/ruby-kind-of-vs-instance-of-vs-is-a</a></p><h1 id="一个有趣的小姐姐的博客（应该是小姐姐）"><a href="#一个有趣的小姐姐的博客（应该是小姐姐）" class="headerlink" title="一个有趣的小姐姐的博客（应该是小姐姐）"></a>一个有趣的小姐姐的博客（应该是小姐姐）</h1><p><a href="https://xguox.me/rails-render-collection.html/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://xguox.me/rails-render-collection.html/</a></p><h1 id="给自己的科普"><a href="#给自己的科普" class="headerlink" title="给自己的科普"></a>给自己的科普</h1><p>想找一个日期控件在rails中使用，功能是支持只选择年和月，终于找到一个喜欢的，转成了scss，发布到服务器的时候说js中有eval很危险，违反了CSP。<br><a href="https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/contentSecurityPolicy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/contentSecurityPolicy</a><br><a href="https://div.io/topic/1669" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://div.io/topic/1669</a><br><a href="https://lavas.baidu.com/pwa/engage-retain-users/add-to-home-screen/introduction" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://lavas.baidu.com/pwa/engage-retain-users/add-to-home-screen/introduction</a><br><a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hans/Eval" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hans/Eval</a><br><a href="http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2012/06/sass.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2012/06/sass.html</a><br><a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000005646206" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000005646206</a></p><h1 id="rails项目里面-View中的response-to"><a href="#rails项目里面-View中的response-to" class="headerlink" title="rails项目里面 View中的response_to"></a>rails项目里面 View中的response_to</h1><p>在项目的后台管理页面中，做了一个用户月账单，需要支持excel导出功能，所以用到这个语句<br><a href="https://ruby-china.org/topics/13771" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ruby-china.org/topics/13771</a></p><h1 id="Ruby中的map"><a href="#Ruby中的map" class="headerlink" title="Ruby中的map"></a>Ruby中的map</h1><p>看《松本行弘的程序世界》中发现Ruby里面好多别名啊，比如map就是collect的别名，类似的上面提到的那个问题中is_a?是kind_of?的别名<br>有一天突然后知后觉想知道map是个什么方法<br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12084507/what-does-the-map-method-do-in-ruby" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12084507/what-does-the-map-method-do-in-ruby</a></p><h1 id="rails中输出excel的格式调整"><a href="#rails中输出excel的格式调整" class="headerlink" title="rails中输出excel的格式调整"></a>rails中输出excel的格式调整</h1><p>在找调整格式的方法时候发现自己找答案的姿势还是应该改进，找了半天才找到权威那个<br><a href="http://www.voidcn.com/article/p-wbylgbcc-ez.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.voidcn.com/article/p-wbylgbcc-ez.html</a><br><a href="https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/ruby-spreadsheet/Spreadsheet/Format" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/ruby-spreadsheet/Spreadsheet/Format</a><br><a href="https://hlee.iteye.com/blog/356510" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hlee.iteye.com/blog/356510</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/9e1e1db83f6d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/9e1e1db83f6d</a><br><a href="http://spreadsheet.rubyforge.org/Spreadsheet/Format.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://spreadsheet.rubyforge.org/Spreadsheet/Format.html</a></p><h1 id="N-1-Query"><a href="#N-1-Query" class="headerlink" title="N+1 Query"></a>N+1 Query</h1><p>在掘金上看了一个老哥“聊聊Ruby”的文章，了解了一下什么是 N+1 Query<br>另外medium.com这个站也很有意思，姑且叫它M站吧<br><a href="https://sdk.cn/news/2532" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://sdk.cn/news/2532</a><br><a href="https://medium.com/@bretdoucette/n-1-queries-and-how-to-avoid-them-a12f02345be5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://medium.com/@bretdoucette/n-1-queries-and-how-to-avoid-them-a12f02345be5</a></p><h1 id="CodeDay"><a href="#CodeDay" class="headerlink" title="CodeDay"></a>CodeDay</h1><p><a href="https://codeday.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://codeday.me/</a></p><h1 id="rails-日期相关"><a href="#rails-日期相关" class="headerlink" title="rails 日期相关"></a>rails 日期相关</h1><p>在日期控件里挣扎不出来的那几天。后来发现问题不日历不显示，而是鼠标悬停后日历的弹出位置不对，被页面上的其他部件盖住了。这个问题还没解决，前端还是不熟<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42428631/article/details/80876157" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42428631/article/details/80876157</a><br><a href="https://codeday.me/bug/20190225/682893.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://codeday.me/bug/20190225/682893.html</a><br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10294430/rails-adding-an-undefined-attribute-to-form-tag" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10294430/rails-adding-an-undefined-attribute-to-form-tag</a></p><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 先写这个，后面的慢慢总结吧。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 马上离职了，本来打算实习整整两个月的，学校答辩的日期定下了，所以提前几天走。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 每次实习都是很好的学习机会。学习还是要靠自己的。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 希望你越来越棒</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 毕竟他说了，你超级棒的</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
