    <title>每周总结 定时发送邮件</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/05/14/%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93-%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/05/14/%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93-%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%91%E9%80%81%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6/</id>
    <published>2019-05-14T10:41:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-14T10:47:10.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>于时初春令月，气淑风和<br>啊呜，一口好吃的嫩绿<br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="rails定时发送邮件"><a href="#rails定时发送邮件" class="headerlink" title="rails定时发送邮件"></a>rails定时发送邮件</h1><ul><li><p>用到的技术：ActiveMailer、gem whenever、cronbtab、rake</p></li><li><p>最初的问题是定时任务默认的环境是producution，需要改成development，可以在schedule.rb中设置 set :environment, :development 使用gem：whenever时手动修改cron list没用，因为whenever –update-crontab（或者whenever -i）时会重新将schedule.rb文件重新执行生成新的cron list, 手动改动的版本就不会被保存会被覆盖。只要决定了使用gem，就要基于gem修改了，因为gem在顶层之上。看错误日志还是可以看crontab的，linux会默认关掉log，需要手动将那行设置的注释去掉（sudo gedit /etc/rsyslog.d/50-default.conf），并且本地可能没有安装邮件服务，需要安装（sudo apt-get install postfix   sudo service postfix start）。也可以在schedule.rb中设置错误日志的输出　set :output, {:error =&gt; ‘~/desktop/z.error.log’, :standard =&gt; ‘~/desktop/z.standard.log’}另外，如果你的rails框架是使用rvm或者rbenv安装的，那么cron 会找不到bundle命令，手动cron list中添加bundle路径的方式不可取，可以在schedule.rb中添加　ENV.each { |k, v| env(k, v) }　</p></li><li><p>总结：查官方文档；检查错误日志；google前人经验；同样一个gem的许多功能和需要的配置在常常就一个文件里面就可以搞定，比如定时任务的schedule.rb</p></li></ul><h1 id="在网上找到的方法和答案"><a href="#在网上找到的方法和答案" class="headerlink" title="在网上找到的方法和答案"></a>在网上找到的方法和答案</h1><ul><li>基本发邮件功能<br><a href="https://ruby-china.github.io/rails-guides/action_mailer_basics.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ruby-china.github.io/rails-guides/action_mailer_basics.html</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/b7a3f209c4b3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/b7a3f209c4b3</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/fedf0484f469" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/fedf0484f469</a><br><a href="https://www.zybuluo.com/rickyChen/note/362077" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zybuluo.com/rickyChen/note/362077</a></li><li>gem letter-opener<br><a href="https://github.com/ryanb/letter_opener/issues/1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/ryanb/letter_opener/issues/1</a></li><li>定时任务crontab和gem whenever和Rake<br><a href="https://medium.com/@pk60905/%E5%9C%A8ruby%E5%92%8Crails%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84rake%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-2eeefe99d7ce" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://medium.com/@pk60905/%E5%9C%A8ruby%E5%92%8Crails%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84rake%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-2eeefe99d7ce</a><br><a href="https://launchschool.com/blog/cron-jobs-and-rails" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://launchschool.com/blog/cron-jobs-and-rails</a><br><a href="https://ruby-china.org/topics/27846" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ruby-china.org/topics/27846</a><br><a href="https://github.com/javan/whenever" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/javan/whenever</a><br><a href="https://www.iteye.com/topic/182472" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.iteye.com/topic/182472</a><br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7548730/cron-job-not-working-in-whenever-gem?noredirect=1&amp;lq=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7548730/cron-job-not-working-in-whenever-gem?noredirect=1&amp;lq=1</a><br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/43257021/start-crond-service-on-ubuntu-16-04" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/43257021/start-crond-service-on-ubuntu-16-04</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/8046ed8fb5ae" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/8046ed8fb5ae</a></li><li>设置并查找日志，解决问题<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/liaoyanyunde/article/details/86572370" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/liaoyanyunde/article/details/86572370</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/tanzuozhev/article/details/50784165" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/tanzuozhev/article/details/50784165</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_37186127/article/details/78862419" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_37186127/article/details/78862419</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/disappearedgod/article/details/43191693" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/disappearedgod/article/details/43191693</a><br><a href="https://my.oschina.net/leejun2005/blog/1788342" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://my.oschina.net/leejun2005/blog/1788342</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qfikh/article/details/78202449" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/qfikh/article/details/78202449</a><br><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/31118033/could-not-find-rake-using-whenever-rails" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/31118033/could-not-find-rake-using-whenever-rails</a><br><a href="https://github.com/javan/whenever/issues/656" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/javan/whenever/issues/656</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
