    <published>2019-05-14T10:37:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-14T10:48:03.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>“The three virtues of a programmer: laziness, impatience, and hubris” — Larry Wall<br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="Ruby-鸭子类型语言"><a href="#Ruby-鸭子类型语言" class="headerlink" title="Ruby - 鸭子类型语言"></a>Ruby - 鸭子类型语言</h1><p><a href="https://www.ctolib.com/topics-37919.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.ctolib.com/topics-37919.html</a></p><h2 id="推荐书目"><a href="#推荐书目" class="headerlink" title="推荐书目"></a>推荐书目</h2><p>Practical Object-Oriented Design in Ruby, from Sandi Metz<br>Confident Ruby, from Avdi Grimm<br>Object on Rails, 同样来自 Avdi Grimm</p><h2 id="开源项目与资源"><a href="#开源项目与资源" class="headerlink" title="开源项目与资源"></a>开源项目与资源</h2><p><a href="https://www.ctolib.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.ctolib.com/</a></p><h1 id="运算符"><a href="#运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符"></a>运算符</h1><p>比如这个 ||=<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/lihuan974683978/article/details/8686297" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/lihuan974683978/article/details/8686297</a></p><h1 id="awesome-gem"><a href="#awesome-gem" class="headerlink" title="awesome gem"></a>awesome gem</h1><p><a href="https://github.com/markets/awesome-ruby/blob/master/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/markets/awesome-ruby/blob/master/README.md</a></p><h1 id="Cookie、Session，Devise"><a href="#Cookie、Session，Devise" class="headerlink" title="Cookie、Session，Devise"></a>Cookie、Session，Devise</h1><p>在做代理登录功能时用到的，了解一下<br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/20818699" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/20818699</a></p><h1 id="sidekiq任务调度流程分析（先马，后面了解多一些再仔细看）"><a href="#sidekiq任务调度流程分析（先马，后面了解多一些再仔细看）" class="headerlink" title="sidekiq任务调度流程分析（先马，后面了解多一些再仔细看）"></a>sidekiq任务调度流程分析（先马，后面了解多一些再仔细看）</h1><p><a href="https://ruby-china.org/topics/31470" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ruby-china.org/topics/31470</a></p><h2 id="关于读源码的建议"><a href="#关于读源码的建议" class="headerlink" title="关于读源码的建议"></a>关于读源码的建议</h2><ul><li>带着问题去阅读，效率通常很高；</li><li>读的过程中适当放弃无关细节，只追击与问题相关的线索；</li><li>有些文档中没有提及的配置项，往往都藏匿在代码之中；</li><li>只有充分了解了工具的运行机制，在遇到问题调优的时候才能得心应手。</li></ul><h1 id="错误处理机制"><a href="#错误处理机制" class="headerlink" title="错误处理机制"></a>错误处理机制</h1><p><a href="https://medium.com/@pk60905/rails%E7%9A%84%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6begin-rescue%E5%92%8Cexception-ab71156a24a2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://medium.com/@pk60905/rails%E7%9A%84%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6begin-rescue%E5%92%8Cexception-ab71156a24a2</a></p><h1 id="见过的最走心的HTTP状态码解释"><a href="#见过的最走心的HTTP状态码解释" class="headerlink" title="见过的最走心的HTTP状态码解释"></a>见过的最走心的HTTP状态码解释</h1><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/hzw05103020/article/details/47276005" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/hzw05103020/article/details/47276005</a></p><h1 id="crontab定时任务"><a href="#crontab定时任务" class="headerlink" title="crontab定时任务"></a>crontab定时任务</h1><p>只用过-l 和 -e<br><a href="https://linuxtools-rst.readthedocs.io/zh_CN/latest/tool/crontab.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://linuxtools-rst.readthedocs.io/zh_CN/latest/tool/crontab.html</a></p><h1 id="ruby时间和日期"><a href="#ruby时间和日期" class="headerlink" title="ruby时间和日期"></a>ruby时间和日期</h1><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/leejeff/article/details/54405873" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/leejeff/article/details/54405873</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42428631/article/details/80876157" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42428631/article/details/80876157</a></p><h1 id="关于Active-Mailer"><a href="#关于Active-Mailer" class="headerlink" title="关于Active Mailer"></a>关于Active Mailer</h1><p>问报错信息有几重要<br><a href="https://ruby-china.org/topics/8918" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://ruby-china.org/topics/8918</a></p><h1 id="puma-基于Ruby的Web-Server服务器"><a href="#puma-基于Ruby的Web-Server服务器" class="headerlink" title="puma 基于Ruby的Web Server服务器"></a>puma 基于Ruby的Web Server服务器</h1><p><a href="https://github.com/puma/puma" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/puma/puma</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/0b8089a3bc56" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/0b8089a3bc56</a></p>]]></content>
    
