    <title>满足闲适又贫穷的一个周末</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/04/07/%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E9%97%B2%E9%80%82%E5%8F%88%E8%B4%AB%E7%A9%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/04/07/%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E9%97%B2%E9%80%82%E5%8F%88%E8%B4%AB%E7%A9%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB/</id>
    <published>2019-04-07T10:22:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-04-07T13:41:54.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Ajax,Linux,Rails，网络… 等等的小碎片知识</p><a id="more"></a><hr><p>毕竟他说，我是一个很棒的人，只是我必须要经常总结❤<br>一点点积累，我就一定是个最棒的人，不辜负</p><hr><h1 id="AJAX"><a href="#AJAX" class="headerlink" title="AJAX"></a>AJAX</h1><p>AJAX其人，是个缩写，全名为Asynchronous JavaScript and XML，用JavaScript执行<strong>异步</strong>网络请求，既然是异步执行的，那么它需要通过回调函数来获得响应。一次HTTP请求会对应一个页面，JavaScript可以使用户在提交HTTP请求之后感觉没有切换页面，但是相应的内容会更新出来。下面看一下是怎样用JavaScript实现AJAX的。</p><h2 id="实现"><a href="#实现" class="headerlink" title="实现"></a>实现</h2><h3 id="现代浏览器对应的AJAX"><a href="#现代浏览器对应的AJAX" class="headerlink" title="现代浏览器对应的AJAX"></a>现代浏览器对应的AJAX</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function success(text) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    var textarea = document.getElementById(&apos;test-response-text&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">    textarea.value = text;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">function fail(code) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    var textarea = document.getElementById(&apos;test-response-text&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">    textarea.value = &apos;Error code: &apos; + code;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">var request = new XMLHttpRequest(); // 新建XMLHttpRequest对象</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">request.onreadystatechange = function () &#123; // 状态发生变化时，函数被回调</span><br><span class="line">    if (request.readyState === 4) &#123; // 成功完成</span><br><span class="line">        // 判断响应结果:</span><br><span class="line">        if (request.status === 200) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            // 成功，通过responseText拿到响应的文本:</span><br><span class="line">            return success(request.responseText);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            // 失败，根据响应码判断失败原因:</span><br><span class="line">            return fail(request.status);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        // HTTP请求还在继续...</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// 发送请求:</span><br><span class="line">request.open(&apos;GET&apos;, &apos;/api/categories&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">request.send();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">alert(&apos;请求已发送，请等待响应...&apos;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="低版本IE中的AJAX和解决办法"><a href="#低版本IE中的AJAX和解决办法" class="headerlink" title="低版本IE中的AJAX和解决办法"></a>低版本IE中的AJAX和解决办法</h3><p>可以看到实现AJAX主要依靠XMLHttpRequest，对于低版本的IE可以换成ActiveXObject。</p><p>为了通用一点还可以这样写<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var request;</span><br><span class="line">if (window.XMLHttpRequest) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    request = new XMLHttpRequest();</span><br><span class="line">&#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    request = new ActiveXObject(&apos;Microsoft.XMLHTTP&apos;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>XMLHttpRequest对象的open()方法有3个参数，第一个指定GET/POST，第二个参数指定URL地址，第三个参数指定是否使用异步，这里当然是True，默认也是True，所以可以不用写。</p><h2 id="安全限制"><a href="#安全限制" class="headerlink" title="安全限制"></a>安全限制</h2><p>默认情况下，JavaScript在发送AJAX请求时，URL的域名必须和当前页面完全一致。即域名、协议、端口号全部要相同。如果就是想访问外域怎么办？</p><h3 id="通过Flash插件发送HTTP请求（不推荐）"><a href="#通过Flash插件发送HTTP请求（不推荐）" class="headerlink" title="通过Flash插件发送HTTP请求（不推荐）"></a>通过Flash插件发送HTTP请求（不推荐）</h3><h3 id="通过在同源域名下架设一个代理服务器来转发"><a href="#通过在同源域名下架设一个代理服务器来转发" class="headerlink" title="通过在同源域名下架设一个代理服务器来转发"></a>通过在同源域名下架设一个代理服务器来转发</h3><p>JavaScript负责将请求发送到代理服务器，代理服务器再将结果返回</p><h3 id="JSONP"><a href="#JSONP" class="headerlink" title="JSONP"></a>JSONP</h3><p>这种方式只能用GET请求，并且要求返回JavaScript，这种跨域方式实际上利用了浏览器语序跨域引用JavaScript资源。这种方式需要在页面上准备好回调函数。<br>有一个小例子在之后提供的参考资料里面。</p><h2 id="其他内容"><a href="#其他内容" class="headerlink" title="其他内容"></a>其他内容</h2><p>我还没看</p><p>以上AJAX内容参考<a href="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/001434446689867b27157e896e74d51a89c25cc8b43bdb3000/001434499861493e7c35be5e0864769a2c06afb4754acc6000#0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">廖雪峰老师的博客</a></p><h2 id="留下个问题，用rails怎么使用AJAX呢？"><a href="#留下个问题，用rails怎么使用AJAX呢？" class="headerlink" title="留下个问题，用rails怎么使用AJAX呢？"></a>留下个问题，用rails怎么使用AJAX呢？</h2><hr><h1 id="Linux-命令之chmod"><a href="#Linux-命令之chmod" class="headerlink" title="Linux 命令之chmod"></a>Linux 命令之chmod</h1><p>在Unix和Linux的各种操作系统下，文件都按“读”(r)、“写”(w)、“运行”(x)设定权限，其中r=4，w=2,x=1.<br>用ls -l命令时得到：<br>-rw-r–r– 1 apple users 2254 2006-05-20 13:47 tt.htm<br>第一个rw表示该登陆用户的权限，第二个r表示他所在组的人的权限，第三个r表示其他人的最高权限。<br>上述命令可以表示为644<br>那么777就是所有人都有最高权限<br>运行下面的命令将使所有人都有最高权限<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod 777 tt.htm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>详情请访问<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/sipher/articles/2429772.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a></p><hr><h1 id="rails"><a href="#rails" class="headerlink" title="rails"></a>rails</h1><h2 id="Jbuilder"><a href="#Jbuilder" class="headerlink" title="Jbuilder"></a>Jbuilder</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/rails/jbuilder#jbuilder" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/rails/jbuilder#jbuilder</a><br><a href="http://ohcoder.com/blog/2015/04/19/jbuilder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://ohcoder.com/blog/2015/04/19/jbuilder/</a></p><h2 id="rake"><a href="#rake" class="headerlink" title="rake"></a>rake</h2><p><a href="https://medium.com/@pk60905/%E5%9C%A8ruby%E5%92%8Crails%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84rake%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-2eeefe99d7ce" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://medium.com/@pk60905/%E5%9C%A8ruby%E5%92%8Crails%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84rake%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-2eeefe99d7ce</a></p><h2 id="Specs（还没用过）"><a href="#Specs（还没用过）" class="headerlink" title="Specs（还没用过）"></a>Specs（还没用过）</h2><p><a href="http://www.betterspecs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://www.betterspecs.org/</a></p><hr><h1 id="云、CDN、IDC"><a href="#云、CDN、IDC" class="headerlink" title="云、CDN、IDC"></a>云、CDN、IDC</h1><p>这部分属于我在科普我自己<br><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/40534161" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zhihu.com/question/40534161</a><br><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/36514327?rf=37353035" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zhihu.com/question/36514327?rf=37353035</a></p><hr><h1 id="关系型数据库中DDL、DML和DCL"><a href="#关系型数据库中DDL、DML和DCL" class="headerlink" title="关系型数据库中DDL、DML和DCL"></a>关系型数据库中DDL、DML和DCL</h1><p><a href="https://blog.51cto.com/jim123/1979202" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.51cto.com/jim123/1979202</a></p><hr><h1 id="git-alias"><a href="#git-alias" class="headerlink" title="git alias"></a>git alias</h1><p><a href="https://juejin.im/post/5c9660c45188252d60192c5e?utm_source=gold_browser_extension" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://juejin.im/post/5c9660c45188252d60192c5e?utm_source=gold_browser_extension</a></p><hr><h1 id="JSON-与字符串格式转换"><a href="#JSON-与字符串格式转换" class="headerlink" title="JSON 与字符串格式转换"></a>JSON 与字符串格式转换</h1><p><a href="https://juejin.im/post/5c9660c45188252d60192c5e?utm_source=gold_browser_extension" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://juejin.im/post/5c9660c45188252d60192c5e?utm_source=gold_browser_extension</a></p><hr><h1 id="TP5-Restful路由设置"><a href="#TP5-Restful路由设置" class="headerlink" title="TP5 Restful路由设置"></a>TP5 Restful路由设置</h1><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/handsome_926/article/details/79698346" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/handsome_926/article/details/79698346</a></p><hr><h1 id="最后马一本书"><a href="#最后马一本书" class="headerlink" title="最后马一本书"></a>最后马一本书</h1><p><a href="https://bbs.hh010.com/thread-525435-1-1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://bbs.hh010.com/thread-525435-1-1.html</a></p><p><img src="/2019/04/07/满足闲适又贫穷的一个周末/hiahia.jpg" alt="兜兜里有好吃的"></p>]]></content>
    
